*ADDING NEW DEVICES*
 Add the device to the :device menu 
 Then add a new menu for device like this
 
  :device name
 CLS
ECHO Stuff goes here 
SET INPUT=
SET /P INPUT=SELECT NUMBER OF OPTION:  

IF /I '%INPUT%'=='1' GOTO x
IF /I '%INPUT%'=='2' GOTO x
IF /I '%INPUT%'=='3' GOTO x
IF /I '%INPUT%'=='4' GOTO x
IF /I '%INPUT%'=='5' GOTO x

